text: Gholam-Hossein Mohseni-Eje'i (, ; born 29 September 1956) is an Iranian conservative politician, Islamic jurist and prosecutor. In July 2021, he became the Chief Justice of Iran. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Chief Justices of Iran Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Isfahan
title: Gholam-Hossein Mohseni-Eje'i
